    public enum Permission
extends java.lang.Enum<Permission>
    , "" Enumerates permissions. These are the permissions that will be grouped to make a permission group. Each function will have Read/Write/None privilege

        public static final Permission JOBTAG
        11/5/2018 - Job permissions are merged into quote permissions. (You need quote permission to do anything with jobs) JOB(null, true, "Functional area: Job"), JOB_READ(JOB, true, "Read-only access to Jobs (Backward Compatibility)"), // this is for backwards compatibility JOB_WRITE(JOB_READ, true, "Can Edit jobs"), // this is for backwards compatibility
